# ============================================================================
# v2 engine + editor — gitignore
# ============================================================================

# ---- Build outputs (binaries — anywhere in the tree) ----------------------
# Executables, DLLs and import-libs are all rebuilt from source by MAKE.bat /
# BUILD.bat; the prebuilt ones under ext/ext-backend-*/x64/ get regenerated
# on first build too. Keeping them out of git keeps the repo small.
*.exe
*.dll
*.lib
*.exp
*.ilk
*.pdb

# ---- Object files (MAKE.bat dumps every translation unit to root) ---------
*.obj
*.o

# ---- Date-stamped cache (native-Sat05232026.obj, backend-...) -------------
native-*.obj
backend-*.obj

# ---- Cook outputs ---------------------------------------------------------
cook.zip
cook*.csv

# ---- Editor auto-generated stubs (per-project, Phase 6a) -------------------
.luarc/
.luarc.json

# ---- User-specific editor state (ImGui dock layout, recent projects, ...) -
.settings.ini

# ---- IDE state ------------------------------------------------------------
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user
*.suo
*.sln.cache
*.opensdf
*.sdf

# ---- Claude Code runtime state (per-session locks, agent outputs) ---------
.claude/

# ---- OS junk --------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
ehthumbs.db
$RECYCLE.BIN/

# ---- Editor backup files --------------------------------------------------
*.swp
*~
*.bak
*.orig

# ---- Build / runtime logs -------------------------------------------------
*.log

# ---- Engine cook-cache (in-place .X.png hidden-prefix from cook() recipe) -
# Example: assets/audio/.foo.mp3 (the engine cook-cache generates hidden-
# prefix files for every cook(path)). MAKE.bat tidy clears them otherwise.
# The pattern is fuzzy so we list the known extensions explicitly.
**/.*.png
**/.*.jpg
**/.*.jpeg
**/.*.tga
**/.*.bmp
**/.*.iqm
**/.*.gltf
**/.*.glb
**/.*.fbx
**/.*.obj
**/.*.lua
**/.*.mp3
**/.*.wav
**/.*.ogg
**/.*.flac
**/.*.mod
**/.*.xm
**/.*.s3m
**/.*.it
**/.*.tmx
**/.*.json5
